Package: blends
Title: Blend Colour Palettes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Hodge", , "davidhodge931@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3868-7501"))
Description: Blends colour palettes using digital blend modes such
    as multiply, screen, and overlay. These methods composite colours and
    palette functions using Porter-Duff alpha compositing for data
    visualisation.
